solution.p:
Acceleration can be obtained by applying Newton's second law of motion with electric force on the electron.

	a \amp = \dfrac{F_e}{m} = \dfrac{qE}{m} 
	 \amp =  \dfrac{1.6\times 10^{-19}\text{ C} \times 300 \text{ N/C}}{ 1.673\times 10^{-27}\text{ kg}} 
	 \amp =  2.87 \times 10^{10}\text{ m/s}^2.
